{"tid":486470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"料千億埋單　馬時亨：沙中綫必超支","createTime":"2017-12-02T01:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T04:55:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"865c2250964e327f857bb60c451766d915ffee76","tid":486470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232181&d=ip1XMQxg6XSL9GoAd3U4dQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=36e167ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232181&h=865e89ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232181</a><br />\n<br />\n料千億埋單　馬時亨：沙中綫必超支<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171202/large/18331044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171202%2Flarge%2F18331044.jpg&h=4e87e33a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬時亨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵主席馬時亨承認，造價798億元的沙中綫定必超支，具體數目會在本月提交政府。立法會議員料沙中綫要近千億「埋單」，要求政府對造價封頂，否則立法會不會通過追加撥款。<br />\n<br />\n議員：不封頂不通過撥款<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨昨出席活動時指，「（沙中綫）超支係肯定，好多因素唔係港鐵可以控制，包括考古、遲交工地情況」，但他拒透露超支金額。立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會昨討論沙中綫進度，港鐵工程總監黃唯銘被議員多次追問超支金額，他只稱估算已到尾聲，正盡量壓縮成本，結果聖誕前後會提交政府。<br />\n<br />\n委員會主席田北辰自行估算，土瓜灣考古及金鐘站工程共超支50億元，而通脹等因素令成本上升一成，即約80億元，加上灣仔填海發現疑似添馬艦殘骸、分域街地盤要移除地下鋼管及會展站工程改動等額外增70億元，料整體超支100至200億元，令造價增至近千億元。他要求政府參考高鐵超支做法，對沙中綫造價封頂，否則立會不會通過追加撥款。<br />\n<br />\n小組委員會亦討論高鐵進展。民主黨林卓廷關注高鐵啟用時長途車可直達內地城市數目，由前局長鄭汝樺至張炳良都指是16個，現減至10個，質疑內地走數。運房局長陳帆表示，16個只屬顧問建議，由於內地高鐵網繁忙，經與國家鐵路總公司商討，目前可落實10個城市。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮"},{"pid":"acda1f120eae72c3f41aaf5624b2fadcd391d047","tid":486470,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:01:17.000Z","msg":"華人政治從來只有抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cd5904537e197d774f1399fa26a7c385b64bcc","tid":486470,"uid":92871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"點解港鐵要政府埋單？"},{"pid":"0db15f2a1bb706c8de561c74954b477348435f82","tid":486470,"uid":15880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"超咩支丫<br />\n走資咪走資囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd727ccc28659103301724914f32bad68cc48626","tid":486470,"uid":45148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"政府買野可以比原價貴20%<br />\n政府請人可以因爲炒左人追番人地人工<br />\n<br />\n這就是香港"},{"pid":"0538c181008aaf8deb729da3b8750f88574a980b","tid":486470,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"政府廢姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3d09deee0e76598f8f20d8c7d8e7c0dbd811b8","tid":486470,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"每次見到馬時亨就好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255389b72204d10615016e97a16e6f161d7eeeda","tid":486470,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"港豬會埋單的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94be44571b7e5a1b01d40573e2eb2a038fe6b596","tid":486470,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:49:15.000Z","msg":"港錢公司"},{"pid":"55c986b976261198a38595301c51401e4a5a9621","tid":486470,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"點解唔係港鐵承擔？"},{"pid":"6e3359e884a73ce3ef70b8575a5527633a42a3e1","tid":486470,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"淋病唔係好打得咩？<br />\n又係得把口？"},{"pid":